  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The Project is expected to promote environmental best practices by utilizing latest technologies in for emission controls, zero water discharge system and waste heat recovery. It is also expected to create around 140 jobs and improve competitiveness of local tire manufacturing industry.</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="1">
